{"tid":1754380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子青龍頭墮樓 當場死亡","createTime":"2019-11-25T07:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:00:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e177dae05e2b299cb68915354ee9ee951ed439be","tid":1754380,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:38:09.000Z","msg":"青龍頭豪景花園，今早近11時，有人從高處墮下，倒臥屋苑對開空地，由途人發現警，警方及救護員到場，證實男子已當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n現場未有檢獲遺書，警方指死者為34歲姓盧男子，相信事件無可疑，確切死因有待驗屍。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會；2389 2222；touch@sbhk.org.hk；24小時(廣東話)<br />\n撒瑪利亞會24小時多語服務：2896 0000；jo@samaritans.org.hk；24小時(廣東話)<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000； admin@sps.org.hk；24小時(廣東話)<br />\n向晴熱線： 18288；fcsc@cfcsc.org.hk；24小時(廣東話)<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1645729/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E9%9D%92%E9%BE%8D%E9%A0%AD%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93-%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1</code></pre>"},{"pid":"050b4843c507f4154441980f576316b48dcb9673","tid":1754380,"uid":40439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"又無可疑"},{"pid":"a2f3a1ca4a8a1ff76abd471f996f82ea20b25764","tid":1754380,"uid":192347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"一定係無可疑"},{"pid":"1a58bc0d315ae5fcf3518d6cea53de176ad0dff3","tid":1754380,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e81b9f